---
name: Phone Number
description: Phone Numbers with optional country code/extension. Note: do not use regex for validating phone numbers!
source: https://digitalfortress.tech/tips/top-15-commonly-used-regex/
flavor: regexp
---

^(?:(?:\(?(?:00|\+)([1-4]\d\d|[1-9]\d?)\)?)?[\-\.\ \\\/]?)?((?:\(?\d{1,}\)?[\-\.\ \\\/]?){0,})(?:[\-\.\ \\\/]?(?:#|ext\.?|extension|x)[\-\.\ \\\/]?(\d+))?$
